Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_bpid::_mbuf_th

0x2000 2FFF

IPD_BPIDX_MBUF_TH = IPD BPID MBUFF Threshold

The number of MBUFFs in use by the BPID, that when exceeded, backpressure will be applied to the BPID.
